OS: Linux Manjaro with KDE
Browser: Chrome

When attempting to delegate/undelegate the modal dissapears, when there is a refresh of the stats while the modal is open.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Go to https://app.arablefi.com/
2. Click on `Validators`.
3. Click on `Delegate/Undelegate`.
4. Wait for the validators list to refreh. This modal disappears.
